### LOW-05: Quiz Questions Generated Fresh on Every [getQuizzes](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/quiz.controller.ts#340-373) Call

| Field | Detail |
|-------|--------|
| **Severity** | 🔵 Low |
| **Component** | [quiz.controller.ts](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/quiz.controller.ts#L15-L27) |
| **Impact** | [shuffleArray](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/quiz.controller.ts#16-24) gives different question order each seed, but no consistency guarantee |

The [buildQuizzesFromBank()](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/quiz.controller.ts#14-192) uses random shuffling. When quizzes are seeded (or reseeded), the question selection and order is random. Two [reseed](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/quiz.controller.ts#247-272) calls produce quizzes with different questions, making quiz IDs and historical analytics potentially inconsistent.

