The template-to-steps conversion logic is copy-pasted in 3 places: [register](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/auth.controller.ts#13-143) (auth.controller), [startLearningPath](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/learningPath.controller.ts#73-157), and [getLearningPath](file:///d:/ai-learning-dashboard/server/src/controllers/learningPath.controller.ts#158-219). Any bug fix must be applied in all 3 locations.

**Remediation:** Extract to a shared function:
```typescript
const convertTemplateToSteps = (template: LearningPathTemplate) => {
    return template.modules.flatMap((module, moduleIdx) => 
        module.milestones.map((milestone, msIdx) => ({ ... }))
    );
};
```

